OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable says that #15
OL,8,Fmillion of funding from Stormont
OL,9,Ffollowing last weeks disorder, is a
OL,10,F"sticking plaster over a gaping wound."
OL,12,FIn an interview with UTV's View from
OL,13,FStormont, Jon Boutcher also said he is
OL,14,Foffended by the Finance Minister's
OL,15,Fquestioning about what the PSNI is
OL,16,Fdoing to help itself when it comes to
OL,17,Ffunding the organisation.
