OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,FThis comes as a further 7 people,
OL,8,Fincluding a 13 year-old-girl, have
OL,9,Fappeared in court charged in
OL,10,Fconnection with rioting over the past
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FLast week's violence stretched the
OL,14,FPSNI with officers responding to
OL,15,Ftrouble in Ballymena, Larne, and
OL,16,FPortadown.
OL,18,FThe Chief Constable said that 64
OL,19,Fofficers have now been injured while
OL,20,F29 arrests have been made,
OL,21,Fhighlighting the scale of the violence.
