OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,F"It's felt that the levels of violence
OL,8,Fon Monday when people were attacking
OL,9,Fthe homes of residents of Ballymena,
OL,10,Fhad the officers not done what they
OL,11,Fdid, and this was specifically given
OL,12,Fto me very emotionally by a fire
OL,13,Fofficer...
OL,15,F"He thinks people could have been
OL,16,Fkilled. All of this behavior has to
OL,17,Fstop. There is no place for it.
