OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,FThe PSNI has a funding gap of around
OL,8,F#21 million and is calling for more
OL,9,Ffunding to cover the significant
OL,10,Fshortfall.
OL,12,FA recruitment process is also under
OL,13,Fway to increase officer numbers over 5
OL,14,Fyears, a process that will cost #200
OL,15,Fmillion.
OL,17,FThe executive is set to give #15
OL,18,Fmillion in additional funding after
OL,19,Flast week's disturbances.
