OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,FThe Chief Constable continued: "#15
OL,8,Fmillion is an amount of money that we
OL,9,Fthink this disorder is costing us.
OL,10,FThat is putting a plaster over a
OL,11,Fgaping wound."
OL,13,F"Since 2010, since the devolvement of
OL,14,Fpolicing to Northern Ireland the PSNI
OL,15,Fhas been let down with regards to
OL,16,Ffunding."
OL,18,FPolice funding was an issue which was
OL,19,Fon the agenda at Stormont this
OL,20,Fafternoon.
