OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,FThe Finance Minister said that while
OL,8,Fhe supported additional funding, he
OL,9,Fasked 'What is the PSNI doing to help
OL,10,Fitself?'
OL,12,FIn response the Chief Constable had
OL,13,Fthis to say back to John O'Dowd: "So
OL,14,FI'm quite offended by that, I'll be
OL,15,Fvery clear.
OL,17,F"We have literally done every possible
OL,18,Fexercise you can to make sure about
OL,19,Fthe efficiency of policing in Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
