OL,3,CPSNI funding for recent trouble is
OL,4,Clike 'sticking a plaster over a gaping
OL,5,Cwound'
OL,7,F"Our numbers have just been cut, this
OL,8,Fisn't on me or my predecessors, this
OL,9,Fis on political decisions not to fund
OL,10,Fthe PSNI.
OL,12,F"Don't give me #5 million to deal with
OL,13,Fa problem that's been created because
OL,14,Fwe haven't got enough police officers.
OL,16,F"Give me the funding to build this
OL,17,Forganization back up so we can keep
OL,18,Fsociety safe here.
